Feature: Managing pricing
  As an owner
  I want to manage the price for a location
  so that my customers are charged adequately

  Background:
    Given a location "Vienna West" exists

  Scenario: Set a new price
    When owner sets the price for location "Vienna West" to 0.45
    Then the price of location "Vienna West" is 0.45

  Scenario: Update an existing price
    Given owner sets the price for location "Vienna West" to 0.45
    When owner updates the price for location "Vienna West" to 0.55
    Then the price of location "Vienna West" is 0.55

  Scenario: Read location pricing
    Given owner sets the price for location "Vienna West" to 0.45
    When owner reads the price for location "Vienna West"
    Then  the price of location "Vienna West" is 0.45
